  "text": ". In view of the (closed) convex hull results presented in Theorems 1 and 2, we believe that the right notion of regularity should depend on the parameterization A 0 + γA 1 as opposed to µA 0 + (1 − µ)A 1 . We compare the running time of the algorithm presented by Jiang and Li [CITATION_1] and the running time of our algorithms in Remark 10.",
